{"id":233003813,"title":"關於柯文哲說出隔離地點","content":"https://youtu.be/CwjZfFlgO4M\n我個人嚴格來說\n針對柯市長所說的隔離地點\n他未經跟緊急應變中心討論是否公開\n這不對的就是事實\n這柯文哲是要自我反省的\n\nhttps://www.facebook.com/136845026417486/posts/2264163140352320/\n不過我發現開始打他的粉專跟底下留言的人\n有部分大頭貼點開個人資訊，曾經有3張選票護台灣的字樣\n我就在想是不是開始在帶風向\n\n如果公布隔離地點確實會造成恐慌\n那如果隱匿了被發現\n那是不是又會造成另一種恐慌？\n所謂的鄰避效應，你不想你家附近蓋垃圾回收場，政府偷偷蓋，身為附近住戶的你是不是會覺得忿忿不平？\n各退一步來說，假如不公開，也是會有人知道隔離區的位置，還是有可能會被揭發出來。\n那如果政府有告知全國人民或是附近居民，哪些區域是隔離區，除了基本的防護措施之外，也建議民眾外出不要到那邊，不是一件很好的事嗎？","excerpt":"我個人嚴格來說，針對柯市長所說的隔離地點，他未經跟緊急應變中心討論是否公開，這不對的就是事實，這柯文哲是要自我反省的，不過我發現開始打他的粉專跟底下留言的人，有部分大頭貼點開個人資訊，曾經有3張選票護","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"fc7574ad-e1df-43d2-bb06-8825c718c065","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-02-02T15:51:02.099Z","updatedAt":"2020-02-02T15:53:53.800Z","commentCount":14,"likeCount":26,"tags":[],"topics":["柯文哲","隔離","地點"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"時事","forumAlias":"trending","school":"中原大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":23},{"id":"aa0d425f-d530-4478-9a77-fe3aedc79eea","count":3}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":false,"withVideos":false,"media":[],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"0ef59fd6-dcbf-4597-8460-37622b7162cb","url":"https://img.youtube.com/vi/CwjZfFlgO4M/hqdefault.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://img.youtube.com/vi/CwjZfFlgO4M/hqdefault.jpg","thumbnail":"https://img.youtube.com/vi/CwjZfFlgO4M/hqdefault.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-02-02T15:51:02.099Z","updatedAt":"2020-02-02T15:53:53.800Z"},{"id":"0ef59fd6-dcbf-4597-8460-37622b7162cb","url":"https://youtu.be/CwjZfFlgO4M","normalizedUrl":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CwjZfFlgO4M","thumbnail":"https://img.youtube.com/vi/CwjZfFlgO4M/hqdefault.jpg","type":"video/youtube","tags"